NOTE TO DB ADMINISTRATORS: Public keys are 217 characters long
all id's are auto-incremented

user
----
id PK
username 
name
birthday
sex
e-mail

category
--------
id PK
type

known_persons
-------------
user_id PK
public_key
category_type

wall_post
---------
id  PK
permission_allowed_to // this list of users are permissible to view the post, its comments and likes
from
to // this can be NULL if the wall is not posted for a specific person
content
comment_id
time

login_logout_log
----------------
username 
login_time 
logout_time

private_message
---------------
message_id PK
from 
to // user_id
content
time 

comment
-------
id PK
post_id FK (From wall_post table)
comment_from
comment_time 

like
----
id PK
post_id FK
like_from

